snippet.title: NCFC 2014 Sneak Peek - Luigi and the Quest for Nothing 2
snippet.description:
http://www.nintendocfc.com/

A sneak peek at the game "Luigi and the Quest for Nothing 2", which will be at NCFC this year. I play through the first three demo stages.

Stay tuned for more sneak peaks of playable games and demos from NCFC!
